le.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dlive.hkmap.app&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=a9255011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=live.hkmap.app</a><br />\n<br />\n另一個backuphk都好地地<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=io.backuphk.backuphkapp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dio.backuphk.backuphkapp&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuR1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=d650e379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=io.backuphk.backuphkapp</a><br />\n<br />\n解釋亦都唔同，GOOGLE只係話唔應該用正在發生嘅衝突賺錢，而APPLE直接話用作伏擊警察，仲話你係犯罪分子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我們時代的革命」（The Revolution Of Our Times）的手機遊戲，違反Google一貫政策。發言人指Google一向「禁止開發商利用敏感活動設計遊戲，例如嘗試<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">從嚴重且正在發生的衝突或悲劇，透過遊戲賺錢</span></strong>」。<br />\n<br />\n美國蘋果公司周三就已將通報港警行蹤的地圖應用程式「HKmap.live」下架，理由是該程式「違反規則、被<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">用作伏擊警察，及被犯罪分子利用在沒有警方執法的區域犯罪</span></strong>」。"},{"pid":"c6a1aa6ee0ef226a3ce482792d1e676623e2185d","tid":1651640,"uid":9387,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"37cb77c28a7454ea0f8c3a249d7ab2ca7a69a1e9","tid":1651640,"uid":109923,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"bceafb1fc0e63b0fb9b5371df00df4a4d6c23a86","tid":1651640,"uid":226155,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:53:02.000Z","msg":"Apple 下架抗爭apps 就奶共<br />\nGoogoe下架同一個apps 無人提"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:54:10.000Z","msg":"Fake News<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGOOGLE PLAY仲有得下載live.hkmap<br />\n自己上GOOGLE PLAY fact che